content.title: Kuwanika Interface Kuona
content.howToUseTooltip:
Pazasi pane mamwe marongero emuchadenga eiyi node anogona kushandiswa kusarudza mashandiro, akadai sekudzvanya, kuzadza zvinyorwa, nezvimwe.

Iko kukosha kwehunhu kunogona kuve kwakadzokororwa muApp peji. Kana iwe ukasangana nekudzokorora, ndapota kufukidza dzimwe nzira dzekufunga kuti dzisarudze hunhu.

Izwi rakatsvuka rinoratidza kuti kukosha kwehunyanzvi kunodzokororwa, izwi rakasvibira rinoratidza kuti kukosha kwehunhu kwakasiyana mukutsvaga kwepepa razvino, uye izwi dema rinoratidza kuti hapana kuenzanisa kwakadzokororwa.
